picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<br /> \n<h4>직접 스테이킹하기</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio를 통해 사용자는 디앱을 떠나지 않고 ETH를 유동성 스테이킹 제공자인 리도 및 로켓풀에 스테이킹할 수 있습니다. 다른 웹사이트나 안전한 스테이크 방법을 검색하지 않아도 됩니다. MetaMask Portfolio 인터페이스의 '스테이크' 탭에서 리도 및 로켓풀 스마트 계약에 직접 연결할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>또한 최근에는 리도와 Stader Labs를 통해 MATIC 스테이킹*(현재 미국 외 지역 사용자만 사용 가능)*을 활성화했습니다. 주의: MATIC 스테이킹은 이더리움 네트워크에서 이루어집니다.</p>\n<h4>간편한 스테이킹, 인출 및 추적</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>스테이킹이 처음이든 아니든, MetaMask Portfolio를 사용하면 하나의 창에서 스테이킹, 인출, 누적 보상을 쉽게 확인할 수 있습니다. 디앱을 떠나지 않고도 이더리움 네트워크 보안에 기여를 시작하고 그 대가로 보상을 적립할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3>MetaMask Portfolio에서 스테이킹하는 방법</h3>\n<br /> \n<ol>\n<li>MetaMask 지갑을 <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">portfolio.metamask.io</a>에 연결하세요</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/stake?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">\"스테이크\"</a> 버튼을 클릭한 다음 ETH 또는 MATIC 가운데 선택하세요.</li>\n<li>원하는 스테이킹 공급자를 선택하세요.</li>\n<li>스테이킹하려는 ETH 또는 MATIC 수량을 입력하세요. \"월간\" 또는 \"연간\" 가운데 선택하여 해당 수량 스테이킹 시 예상 보상을 확인하세요. 준비가 되었다면 \"검토\"를 클릭하여 스테이킹을 검토하세요.</li>\n<li>검토가 끝났다면 \"확인\"을 선택한 다음 지갑 내 거래에 서명하여 스테이킹 거래를 승인하고 제출하세요.</li>\n<li>거래가 완료되면 보유 카드에 적립된 보상을 확인하세요.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>성공적으로 완료되었습니다! 🦊</p>\n<h4>스테이킹, 공공의 재화</h4>\n<br /> \n<p>MetaMask Portfolio로 사용자는 블록체인 네트워크 보안에 기여하는 탈중앙화된 공공선(Public good)에 참여할 수 있습니다. 또한, 이더리움의 보안과 성장에 직접 기여하고 유동성 스테이킹 공급자로부터 대가로 보상을 받을 수 있습니다. 스테이킹 인출 여부와 관계없이 stETH/rETH/stMATIC/MATICX 토큰을 디파이에서 담보로 사용하거나 다른 토큰으로 교환하는 등 모든 작업을 단일 창에서 처리할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>스테이킹할 준비되었나요? <a href=\"https://metamask.io/portfolio/?utm_source=metamask&#x26;utm_medium=blog&#x26;utm_campaign=feature-articles_content\">metamask.io/portfolio/</a>에서 자세히 알아보세요</p>\n<hr>\n<p><em><strong>MetaMask Portfolio: 웹3의 모든 것을 추적하고 관리하세요</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>MetaMask Portfolio는 웹3.0의 필요를 충족하고 사용자가 모든 것을 제어할 수 있는 사용자 친화적 종합 플랫폼입니다. 대시보드를 통해 매수, 스왑, 브리지, 스테이크 등 모든 활동을 할 수 있습니다. MetaMask Portfolio는 의미 있는 업데이트를 통해 지속적으로 디앱을 개선하고 발전시키기 위해 노력하고 있습니다. 여기를 클릭하여 MetaMask Portfolio와 그 기능을 자세히 알아보세요.</em></p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":"이 단계별 가이드를 통해 MetaMask Portfolio에서 암호화폐를 스테이킹하는 방법을 알아보세요.","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false},"news_bg":{"file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3hGSTCAVrdhSMmLJHSHOWT/94799532e03716ceb32ad39268bef4b0/news-detail-bg.png"}},"news_dark_bg":{"file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/2StKLJf0XE38EyT9GlzQuO/ed29f2ebdc6b99f7ff32175a192133c3/news-detail-dark-bg.png"}},"hubspot":{"contentful_id":"5VZVKtbcRMzaaP77nsz3Fs","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulHubSpotForm"},"title":"Receive our Newsletter","description":null,"portalId":"4795067","formId":"fbfea1e4-e214-4ab2-a98b-964f9a81695a","campaignId":null,"displayTitle":true,"width":null,"customClass":"newsletterOnNewsDetail","customId":null},"latest":{"internal":{"type":"ContentfulLayoutModuleContainer"},"contentful_id":"nO1tqQRjoUDUJfdg2B651","node_locale":"ko","eyebrow":null,"headline":"최신 스토리 계속 읽기","description":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>개발자, 보안 뉴스 등</p>"}},"modules":[{"node_locale":"ko","contentful_id":"6iOGB8Fiab9ilS0jfZ8N5I","fontSize":null,"ctaLink":"/news/","displayText":"모든 게시물","displayTextTreatment":null,"newTab":false,"buttonDisplay":false,"buttonGradient":false,"buttonSecondary":false,"hideButtonIcon":null,"eventLabel":null,"eventCategory":null,"socialLink":null,"showCaretRight":null,"buttonCaretDown":null,"launchDarklyFlag":null,"customClassName":null,"internal":{"type":"ContentfulCta"},"hubSpotForm":null,"embedHTML":null,"downloadBrowsers":null,"mobileCta":null,"alternativeCta":null},{"contentful_id":"1B0wZMveBTSiMJZWu4uunI","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulModuleContainer"},"title":"News > Latest Stories (3 items)","description":null,"numberOfItem":3,"columns":3,"columnType":null,"columnsOnTablet":null,"centerOnTablet":null,"columnsOnMobile":1,"centerOnMobile":null,"contentAlignment":"left","splitModules":false,"displayTitle":false,"isLiquiditySection":false,"isTrustBar":null,"gridModulesGap":"12px","loadMoreMode":null,"loadMoreCta":null,"carouselMode":null,"hasRegionSelector":null,"regionSelectorHeadline":null,"regionSelectorPopupTitle":null,"regionSelectorPopupText":null,"regionListKey":null,"extraData":null,"modules":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}]}],"cta":null,"backgroundColor":"default","displayHeadline":true,"headlineAlignCenter":true,"contentAlignCenter":false,"headlineMarginTop0":null,"paddingTop":"40px","sectionPadding":null,"noPaddingTop":null,"noPaddingBottom":false,"modulesMargin":null,"isTab":false,"moduleId":null,"customClass":"storiesOnNewsDetail","sideImage":null,"backgroundSize":"cover","backgroundImage":null},"latestStories":{"nodes":[{"contentful_id":"7gWB8FZlJfMMD9aqP9WPBt","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNews"},"title":"10 Things You Can Do with MetaMask Portfolio","slug":"10-things-you-can-do-with-metamask-portfolio","subtitle":"Whether you’re an OG or newbie, the Fox is here to make you more powerful in web3. Here are 10 things you can do today in MetaMask Portfolio. ","image":{"title":" 10 Things You Can Do with MetaMask Portfolio","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=webp 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=webp 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/3ioonsghKkND94uL3k7fP8/8a1495747167c8aaa3fcce7c70783fe3/24-09-05_MwM_Blog-Post-10-Things-You-Can-Do-With-Portfolio.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1080}},"publishDate":"September 10, 2024","authors":[{"name":"Clarissa Watson","createProfilePage":true,"profileUrl":"clarissa-watson"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The MetaMask wallet has been around almost as long as web3 itself. Launched in 2016, the Fox has come a long way since then, guided by a mission to connect as many people around the world to the decentralized internet as possible. And we know connecting is just the start - much more than that MetaMask enables you to buy, sell, swap, bridge, stake, and beyond, and it all starts in Portfolio.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/?_gl=1*6m17bz*_gcl_au*NTQwNjYzOTcwLjE3MjQ3NzA0Nzc.\">MetaMask Portfolio</a> is where you get a clear, comprehensive view of your accounts and wallets across all networks. It’s also where your web3 journey begins. Whether you’ve been using MetaMask for years or even minutes, here are ten things you can do in Portfolio right now:</p>\n<h3>Ten ways MetaMask Portfolio makes you powerful in web3</h3>\n<br />\n<p><strong>1. Manage your digital assets and track performance in the dashboard:</strong> Easily view and manage all your digital assets including Ethereum tokens (ERC-20) and non-fungible tokens (NFTs), all from a single, unified interface. Keep an eye on your portfolio's performance over time, with insights into asset distribution, historical transactions, and overall value trends. Remember you can view the balances of any public Ethereum address or ENS. You can also view which airdrops you’re eligible for by using the claim airdrop feature.</p>\n<p>How to use the Dashboard on MetaMask Portfolio:</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XWPizSkhFp4?si=vA8sLicm8Dsct7-z\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p><br /> <br> <br></p>\n<p><strong>2. Do your taxes:</strong> Yes, that’s correct – you can do your crypto taxes directly from Portfolio. All you have to do is connect your wallet and you’ll receive 10% off your tax services with recommended providers like CoinTracker, CoinLedger, ZenLedger, Crypto Tax Calculator, and Koinly:</p>\n<p><img src=\"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4aDE3uJ0OjZgg5Odon5fc0/ed0f8bb99423abb8500b724ab12d5e0b/image1.png\" alt=\" 10 Things You Can Do with MetaMask Portfolio feature image\"></p>\n<br />\n<p><strong>3. Connect to dapps and explore web3:</strong> Access and engage with all the dapps web3 has to offer directly through Portfolio: from decentralized finance (DeFi) platforms like <a href=\"https://aave.com/\">Aave</a>, <a href=\"https://uniswap.org/\">Uniswap</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.renzoprotocol.com/\">Renzo</a>, gaming dapps such as <a href=\"https://www.hyperplay.xyz/\">HyperPlay</a> to NFT marketplaces like <a href=\"https://opensea.io/\">OpenSea</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>4. Swap tokens:</strong> Use the <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/swap\">built-in swap feature</a> to trade tokens directly within Portfolio, leveraging the best available rates across multiple decentralized exchanges (DEXs).</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/q9uG6Ra-w54?si=DiRuOeEZh4tUpZnS\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p><br /> <br></p>\n<p><strong>5. Connect to multiple networks:</strong> Beyond Ethereum, MetaMask supports various Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM)-compatible networks, allowing users to switch between networks like Binance Smart Chain, Polygon, <a href=\"https://linea.build/\">Linea</a>, and more.</p>\n<p><strong>6. Buy and sell cryptocurrency:</strong> Buy cryptocurrencies directly within MetaMask Portfolio using traditional payment methods such as bank transfers or credit cards, and through integrations with third-party providers like Paypal and Revoult. And if you’re ready to sell, Portfolio has you covered, simply connect your wallet and select your method to cash out.</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OtoymxLYQYU?si=x6sOzk8H5wfA_Mr1\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<br />\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IDoCq5vKCBQ?si=nQ6FoN1apO9seMCM\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p><br /> <br></p>\n<p><strong>7. Integrate with your hardware wallet:</strong> Enhance your security by connecting MetaMask to hardware wallets like Ledger or Trezor from Portfolio, combining the convenience of MetaMask with the robust security of cold storage.</p>\n<p><strong>8. Customize privacy settings:</strong> Adjust your privacy settings to your preference, including setting up a custom RPC for specific networks, managing connected sites, and reviewing permissions. Learn more about how to configure your privacy settings <a href=\"https://metamask.io/news/latest/product-spotlight-privacy-preserving-features-in-metamask/\">here.</a></p>\n<p><strong>9. Participate in staking:</strong> Stake your crypto directly through MetaMask Portfolio, participating in the decision-making processes of various protocols and earning rewards. In Portfolio, there are three options for staking, Validator, Pooled, and <a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/stake?tab=liquid\">Liquid</a>. The below tutorials show you how easy it is to start staking based on your preference.</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MQRwcnQVsOE?si=ZT1ykhcORwR4DYXl\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<br />\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eHEymH5s97o?si=ahioErY_gO8k3xDx\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p><br /> <br></p>\n<p><strong>10. Bridge tokens:</strong> Bridging tokens on MetaMask refers to the process of transferring digital assets or tokens from one blockchain network to another using MetaMask as the interface for the transaction. Bridging tokens is a powerful feature in Portfolio that enhances the interoperability between different blockchain networks, enabling users to leverage the unique advantages of each network.</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/r1rwvBWk5XU?si=twN-RTUS1qioHW3l\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<br />\n<h3><strong>Coming soon in Portfolio</strong></h3>\n<br />\n<p>Transfer assets from centralized exchanges (CEXs) like Coinbase and Binance directly to your MetaMask wallet, or between different accounts within MetaMask itself, with enhanced security and ease. Stay tuned for this feature coming soon in Portfolio.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://portfolio.metamask.io/\">MetaMask Portfolio</a> not only simplifies the management of digital assets but also opens up a world of possibilities for users to explore and engage with the decentralized ecosystem, all while maintaining a high level of security and user control. Get started today.</p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":"10 Things You Can Do with MetaMask Portfolio","metaDescription":"Whether you’re an OG or newbie, the Fox is here to make you more powerful in web3. Here are 10 things you can do today in MetaMask Portfolio. ","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false},{"contentful_id":"1MDnahCtyM5a3gqxJKsPUU","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNews"},"title":"MetaMask UI Update: Signature Redesign","slug":"metamask-ui-update-signature-redesign","subtitle":"MetaMask Extension's new UI update makes reviewing signature requests simpler and clearer.","image":{"title":"MetaMask UI Update","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=webp 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=webp 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=webp 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png?w=480&h=270&q=80&fm=png 480w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png?w=960&h=540&q=80&fm=png 960w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/6iqaCFcCH059G2ZnSK1Sdq/ca1910ada682ac265125da7fcf82eb0b/24_08_13_MwM_Blog-Post-Signature-Redesign.png?w=1920&h=1080&q=80&fm=png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1080}},"publishDate":"September 9, 2024","authors":[{"name":"Amit Vadi","createProfilePage":false,"profileUrl":"amit-vadi"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>We’re excited to introduce our latest UI update for MetaMask Extension, aimed at improving the readability of signature requests.</p>\n<p>For All Users: Whether you're new to MetaMask or a seasoned user, you'll notice a fresh, more visually pleasing look when receiving signature requests. This update makes it easier to understand and review the actions you're about to approve.</p>\n<p>How It Works: Starting with v12.2 of the MetaMask Extension, you'll see the redesigned interface for Permit and Sign In With Ethereum signatures. Don't worry if you don't see changes right away—we're rolling this out gradually to ensure a smooth transition.</p>\n<p>In the coming months, we'll be extending this new UI to more signatures, transactions, and our Mobile app. Stay tuned for these updates!</p>\n<p>To keep up with the latest on this rollout and other updates, follow us on Twitter <a href=\"https://x.com/MetaMaskSupport\">@MetaMaskSupport</a> and keep an eye on our Support Channel.</p>\n<p>Want to Learn More? Dive deeper into the world of MetaMask signatures by checking out our <a href=\"https://support.metamask.io/getting-started/what-is-a-signature-in-metamask/\">support article</a>.</p>\n<p>Embrace clarity and enjoy peace of mind. Happy signing!</p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":"MetaMask UI Update: Signature Redesign","metaDescription":"MetaMask Extension's new UI update makes reviewing signature requests simpler and clearer.","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false},{"contentful_id":"cCKfUJxfV3LpnWwHniezZ","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNews"},"title":"MetaMask UX Update: Improved Token Insights","slug":"metamask-ux-update-improved-token-insights","subtitle":"The new update provides a comprehensive understanding of your crypto assets with 24-hour percentage changes and detailed financial data per ERC20 token.","image":{"title":"Token insight feature image","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png"},"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png?w=478&h=267&q=80&fm=webp 478w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png?w=956&h=535&q=80&fm=webp 956w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png?w=1912&h=1070&q=80&fm=webp 1912w","sizes":"(min-width: 1912px) 1912px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png?w=1912&h=1070&q=80&fm=png","srcSet":"https://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png?w=478&h=267&q=80&fm=png 478w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png?w=956&h=535&q=80&fm=png 956w,\nhttps://images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4DPkygNwi4c42kfLfumj61/d789aca2bf866ee6f4ff167a7681fb99/Screenshot_2024-09-04_at_4.09.26_AM__1_.png?w=1912&h=1070&q=80&fm=png 1912w","sizes":"(min-width: 1912px) 1912px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","width":1920,"height":1074}},"publishDate":"September 4, 2024","authors":[{"name":"Amit Vadi","createProfilePage":false,"profileUrl":"amit-vadi"}],"content":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>We are excited to introduce two important enhancements to our token management feature:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>24-Hour percentage changes in token lists</li>\n<li>Detailed financial data in token details</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Your token lists will now display 24-hour percentage changes, allowing you to quickly assess price trends directly in MetaMask. You can also access detailed financial data, including price charts and market cap information, when you click on your ERC20 tokens.</p>\n<p>This is now available in <a href=\"https://metamask.io/download/\">MetaMask Extension</a> and is coming soon to Mobile.</p>\n<p>The 24-hour percentage change will be visible in the main asset list view, while detailed financial data can be found by clicking on the specific ERC20 tokens.</p>\n<p>Whether you're a seasoned investor or new to crypto, having easy access to price trends and detailed financial information helps you manage your portfolio more effectively. You can learn more about it in our <a href=\"https://support.metamask.io/managing-my-tokens/custom-tokens/how-to-display-tokens-in-metamask#token-details\">support article</a>.</p>\n<p>Stay tuned for further updates. Enjoy!</p>"}},"categories":[{"contentful_id":"3tE0tpmPMGsXezpOhKyWGO","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulNewsCategory"},"name":"최신","slug":"latest"}],"metaTitle":"MetaMask UX Update: Improved Token Insights","metaDescription":"The new update provides a comprehensive understanding of your crypto assets with 24-hour percentage changes and detailed financial data per ERC20 token.","canonicalUrl":null,"isPrivate":false}]},"footer":{"contentful_id":"75bFgEllkMxpVsY8wWlroX","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulLayoutFooter"},"logo":{"contentful_id":"6fkPzzTMo3IoMKGMshuSVD","node_locale":"ko","internal":{"type":"ContentfulLogo"},"title":"MetaMask Logo","logo":{"title":"mm-logo","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/4zJfzJbG3kTDSk5Wo4RJI1/1b363263141cf629b28155e2625b56c9/mm-logo.svg"},"gatsbyImageData":null},"logoDarkMode":{"title":"mm-logo-white","description":"","file":{"url":"//images.ctfassets.net/9sy2a0egs6zh/2qy1wS5MmZOXkXn9yFlGJp/f3797a512c283e6f71450a